Package org.framed.orm.ui.action

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConstraintsDialog
    A dialog class for creating a dialog, which let the user choose the Relations from type total, cyclic, acyclic, reflexive and irreflexive for a Relation from type relationship.
    CreateAttributeOperationAction
    A action for creating a operations and attributess.
    FulfillRolesAction
    This action is for adding to a Relation from type fulfillment the Shapess from type roletype and rolegroup ,which the source of the fufillment fulfills.
    RelationshipConstraintsAction
    This action is for adding/removing Relations from type total, cyclic, acyclic, reflexive and irreflexive to/from a Relation from type realtionship through a ConstraintsDialog.
    RolesDialog
    A dialog class for creating a dialog, which let the user choose the Shapes from type roletype and rolegroup he wants to add or to remove from a Relation from type fulfillment.
    StepAction
    This action is the super action for the different stepactions, which all have almost the same code for the method calculateEnabled() and the method run().
    StepInAction
    This action is for stepping in a Compartment or in a Grouping without opening a new page or a new tab.
    StepInNewPageAction
    This action is for stepping in a Compartment or in a Grouping with opening a new page.
    StepInNewTabAction
    This action is for stepping in a Compartment or in a Grouping with opening a new tab.
    StepOutAction
    This action is for stepping out of a Compartment or a Grouping without opening a new page or a new tab.
